Hi - 

It could just has been an off game for me, that being said. I play alot of Mundo - mostly the Mundo Mundo skin and my last hitting is mostly on point. The other day i decided to switch to the Executioner Mundo skin and I happen to noticed what seemed like a slight delay in his auto attacking. When I would normally go in for a kill during laning - it seems like mundo, with that skin, would take a fraction of a second longer to &#039;connect&#039; with the minion - resulting in a misfire. 

Just my 2 cents. {{champion:36}}
